The new edition of this best-selling book tells you how to: give impressive answers to over 200 interview questions; deal with interview nerves and project total confidence; pass psychometric tests, competency-based questions, and assessment centres; avoid the traps that interviewers lay for unwary job seekers; and, turn every interview question to your advantage...........
